Game Design Document
- what is it called? - Kung Fu
- goal of game - defeating all the villians and completing all 3 levels without running out of lifespan
- brief story - the kung fu master is back to get revenge on the zombies for killing his son so if he completes all 3 levels then his son will be reborn - 
 - characters  - kung fu master - he can punch and kick enemies -  zombie - sucks the life out of you so your life level decreases - 
 - non playing characters - zombies  - suck life out of you
 - how to make game engaging  - by making the playing character punch and kick the enemies the player of the game will have to be dialed in to focus so that they don't die
